{"tid":2007083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好因憤怒而亂部署","createTime":"2020-05-08T07:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T08:59:09.000Z","uid":199893,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b378d915fb25beea2f99279f2dcc377ad133f5e6","tid":2007083,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"相信大家都好憤怒<br />\n我都係<br />\n但千祈唔好因為憤怒而亂咁行<br />\n亂咁火魔 亂咁裝修 亂咁上街<br />\n<br />\n和理Sing喺最近已經非常奏效<br />\n用呢招好有效達到我地嘅目標<br />\n所以<br />\n我宣布 十八區商場和你Sing開始<br />\n和理非出嚟行商場啦 無裝就夠 淨係用把口出招已經可以<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0719645ab23403380fb9788d5f67eade1c200024","tid":2007083,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"請出街"},{"pid":"54bf885962ea95da7e522e3ea1ef42e4d84710c9","tid":2007083,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"靜靜地出街<br />\n大大聽抱怨"},{"pid":"5e97a704fb5b39daff9d02bd6993f94e6f73aaa8","tid":2007083,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"千萬真係唔好因憤怒而亂行<br />\n而家冇怒氣值夠高就有大技出架"},{"pid":"fe0ed31417ca3808cea6d4393e81c4618523b9e8","tid":2007083,"uid":125026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"大致認同，但唔同意十八區<br />\n講真，動員咗「十八」區咁多次，有幾多次真係區區有人？係得實施禁蒙面法果日咁大把，平時就算搞五區、六區開花都好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e72246b8443e6f9643eab238da6b061f1ce4e6c","tid":2007083,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff6f103e